    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/eb33c50e3155034de6495033188f4272.avif?t=1772048431\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras_big/eb33c50e3155034de6495033188f4272.webp?t=1772048431 width=1560 height=228 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Mainframe is lost, and you might be the only person still able to fight the MegaCorps. Lucky you! <strong>Your mission: dismantle capitalism one computer server at a time.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/9204225121d7a251fbb326380ba03548.poster.avif?t=1772048431\" width=1170 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/9204225121d7a251fbb326380ba03548.webm?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/9204225121d7a251fbb326380ba03548.mp4?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Data is currency, money, moola 🤑 The MegaCorps have too much info on me, you, and everyone. You’ll be taking it back. After all, progs aren’t cheap!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/aa24539a040a84314e45cd5efd949bf4.poster.avif?t=1772048431\" width=1170 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/aa24539a040a84314e45cd5efd949bf4.webm?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/aa24539a040a84314e45cd5efd949bf4.mp4?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progs are powers, and the MegaCorps control them all. You'll be stealing their code, and using it against them. Expect consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/31fdabf45f5a6404dd95ceb719069f20.poster.avif?t=1772048431\" width=1170 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/31fdabf45f5a6404dd95ceb719069f20.webm?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/31fdabf45f5a6404dd95ceb719069f20.mp4?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You didn’t think the MegaCorps were going to let you reach the Mainframe without a fight, did you? The cyberstakes are high. Get disconnected too many times, and your mission starts from scratch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/6442fad2399e72bbcb9163a325d8572f.poster.avif?t=1772048431\" width=1170 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/6442fad2399e72bbcb9163a325d8572f.webm?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/6442fad2399e72bbcb9163a325d8572f.mp4?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Big Three’s defenses are strong, Hacker, but you can be stronger. Pick up new tricks on every run, use the MegaCorps' progs to change the world, and find that Mainframe!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/2feeae2232263f15fa0c946564d79b30.poster.avif?t=1772048431\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/2feeae2232263f15fa0c946564d79b30.webm?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304110/extras/2feeae2232263f15fa0c946564d79b30.mp4?t=1772048431\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
